## Ingredients
- Cheese
- 2 sticks butter (16 tbsp)
- 2 tbsp poppy seeds
- 2 tbsp worcestershire sauce
- 2 tbsp mustard
- 4 tbsp brown sugar (optional)
- 6-8 hamburger buns

## Instructions
1. Combine melted butter, poppy seeds, worcestershire sauce, mustard, and (optionally) brown sugar
2. Pour over sandwiches and refigerate for at least 4 hours
3. Bake at 325 for 25 minutes covered and 5 min uncovered

